OL,3,CSpike in number of sexual assaults at
OL,4,Cmental health facilities in 2024 `
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FThere was an increase in the number of
OL,8,Freported sexual assaults at mental
OL,9,Fhealth facilities last year, a new
OL,10,Freport has found.
OL,12,FIn its annual report, the Mental
OL,13,FHealth Commission (MHC) found that in
OL,14,Frelation to the criminal events
OL,15,F(sexual assault) category, there was a
OL,16,Fmarked annual increase in the number
OL,17,Fof centre incidents.
OL,19,FIt found that last year there were 76
OL,20,Freported incidents, compared with 42
OL,21,Fin 2023 and 12 in 2022.
