OL,7,FIn a statement, a spokeswoman for the
OL,8,FHSE said: "The report confirms the
OL,9,Fpositive move towards human rights-
OL,10,Fbased standards of mental healthcare
OL,11,Fand that the majority of approved
OL,12,Fcentres are substantially compliant.
OL,14,F"The trend of compliance at a national
OL,15,Flevel remains positive, with six
OL,16,Fapproved centres achieving 100%
OL,17,Fcompliance, four of which were HSE
OL,18,Ffacilities.
OL,20,F"Overall compliance across HSE adult
OL,21,Fcentres in 2024 was over 80%.
